{"tid":1759484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉虎車藏刀棍就無事，細路持鐳射筆變槍","createTime":"2019-11-27T16:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T09:32:08.000Z","uid":236348,"like":138,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0a14bb4dd3bf2e179fb0c067202596120b1957","tid":1759484,"uid":236348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"阿sir 做嘢唔使你教，差佬辦案我真係識條鐵。<br />\n<br />\n葉虎成車都係鐵通武士刀，有晒地址姓名乜事都冇。唔好話拉，連請佢去警署問下話都冇。<br />\n<br />\n相反，細路身上搜到鐳射筆，就係都話佢係鐳射槍，係攻擊性武器，上到庭，一年半載監禁走唔甩。<br />\n<br />\n阿sir 從來冇令我失望，指鹿為馬顛倒是非黑白技倆果然係Asia finest."},{"pid":"fa685fcd71d0a565fff4ff71abf44188eff5ddb2","tid":1759484,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:18:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff9e02685e9ccaed0ae42d47d7b362646ab48f93","tid":1759484,"uid":236348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:18:16.000Z","msg":"曱近平"},{"pid":"1b87b178e5b1b478b6f949b936c26de7bb52fa9e","tid":1759484,"uid":236348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:18:49.000Z","msg":"其實大家係咪淡忘晒件事？一路冇人提嘅？"},{"pid":"af0a0c67e74623667fbcf6715ae9bd6a15014bbc","tid":1759484,"uid":236348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"曱近平"},{"pid":"3974101d9d00309cda80e0813ac4a2d90aab9bb3","tid":1759484,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"2eb9c03dc09383f373e05396dcb11aef663dcfc4","tid":1759484,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"13e9a39f5c558d11d091a421e4c624acf6fc8d8b","tid":1759484,"uid":14341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8259c68540267bc